snippet.title: Project Thalassa - Game Teaser Trailer Video
snippet.description:
Project Thalassa is a first-person psychological drama, where you play as a deep-sea diver in an era reminiscent of early 1900s.

Go through the journey of a diver desperately seeking to understand the mystery of their sunken ship, the reasons for their trauma by going back to the roots of the events. 

Visit www.projectthalassa.com

Music by Ragnhild Tronsmo Haugland

For more info on Project Thalassa.
Subscribe to youtube.com/sareptastudio 
Follow twitter.com/sareptastudio
Buy Merch - COMING SOON

Voice Actors -
Amelia Tyler (twitter.com/AmeliaTyler)
Jay Britton (twitter.com/VoiceJayBritton)

Project Thalassa with the support of the Creative Europe Programme – MEDIA of the European Union
